CashPaymentHint.Default:
When flagged, affects how the payment method will be treated by the system:
- During box operations (deposit, withdrawal, final close), currency denominations will be available for the user to complete;
- Will be included in the calculation for cash limit alert notifications

ManageOtherWaiterOpenTabHint.Default:
Determine whethe a user can manage only its own opentabs or all.
- when **ENABLED** the operator can assign opentabs to anyone and can view other operators' opentabs;
- when **DISABLED** the operator can assign opentabs only to himself and is prevented from viewing other operators' opentabs;
in addition, if the operator is not a "waiter" will be prevented to access opentab functionality.

InvoiceIssue_PeriodHint.Default:
Defines which orders will be selected for invoicing:
- **ANY**: all orders issued (no time filter);
- **DAY**: all orders issued until the day before;
- **WEEK**: all orders issued until the last day of the past week;
- **MONTH**: all orders issued until the last day of the past month.

All options take the order's issueing fiscal date, and relate to the task's execution date/time.

InvoiceIssue_GroupingHint.Default:
Defines how orders should be grouped per invoice:
- **ALL**: 1 invoice per client;
- **MONTH**: 1 invoice per month per client;
- **WEEK**: 1 invoice per week per client;
- **DAY**: 1 invoice per day per client;
- **ORDER**: 1 invoice per order.

ResMaintenance_ResPurge_Hint.Default:
Void un-paid orders, releasing any held resource (ie: limited capacity events). The order selection criteria can be based both on **order creation date** and **visit date**.
Two jobs will be performed: - Void Orders with an incoming performance that are not yet paid; - Void Orders that have been created before a certain time but not yet paid;
**Example (first visit date)**: if current **date** is 10/09/2021 and "**Days from visit date**" parameter is equal 1, the task will void all orders with first visit date wich is BEFORE 12/09/2021. **Example (creation Date)**: if current **fiscal date** is 10/09/2021 and "**Days from creation**" parameter is equal 1, the task will void all orders with creation date which is BEFORE 09/09/2021.
